        "id": 1000008
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-06-08T16:31:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I feel like a separate interface may be better.  That way, it could only be created if necessary.  We also wouldn\u0027t have to worry about what DiagnosticType should be set to for non CPER-type logs.",
